{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1N000476", "chronotag": "1739874690704", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "476", "numeroOrdreDepot": "476", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC0613", "triAmendement": "caaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaawz", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795528", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845407", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA795046", "PA795864", "PA720446", "PA793270", "PA721584", "PA795386", "PA722134", "PA842147", "PA721764", "PA720190"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Rodwell,  Mme&#160;Yadan, M.&#160;Pierre&#160;Cazeneuve, Mme&#160;Liso, M.&#160;Rousset, M.&#160;Terlier, M.&#160;Lef&#232;vre, M.&#160;Fi&#233;vet, M.&#160;Mongardien, Mme&#160;Olivia&#160;Gr&#233;goire et M.&#160;Sorre"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article PREMIER", "articleDesignationCourte": "APR\u00c8S ART. PREMIER", "articleDesignation": "APR\u00c8S L'ARTICLE PREMIER, ins\u00e9rer l'article suivant:", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "Apr\u00e8s", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "true", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0613.asp#D_Article_1er"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>Dans un d&#x00E9;lai d&#x2019;un an &#x00E0; compter de la promulgation de la pr&#x00E9;sente loi, le Gouvernement remet au Parlement un rapport d&#x00E9;taillant les mesures financi&#x00E8;res compensatoires n&#x00E9;cessaires pour assurer la viabilit&#x00E9; du syst&#x00E8;me de retraite en cas d&#x2019;abrogation de la r&#x00E9;forme des retraites de 2023. Ce rapport analyse les impacts financiers de l&#x2019;abrogation de chaque disposition cl&#x00E9;, telles que le report de l&#x2019;&#x00E2;ge l&#x00E9;gal de d&#x00E9;part &#x00E0; la retraite et l&#x2019;augmentation de la dur&#x00E9;e d&#x2019;assurance, ainsi que proposer des solutions de financement alternatives.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; obtenir une &#x00E9;valuation pr&#x00E9;cise des cons&#x00E9;quences financi&#x00E8;res d'une abrogation de la r&#x00E9;forme des retraites de 2023, en particulier concernant le report de l&#x2019;&#x00E2;ge de d&#x00E9;part et l'allongement de la dur&#x00E9;e de cotisation. Une abrogation sans mesures compensatoires mettrait en p&#x00E9;ril l'&#x00E9;quilibre financier du syst&#x00E8;me de retraite. Ce rapport est donc essentiel pour que le Parlement puisse &#x00E9;valuer les solutions de financement et les alternatives de compensation avant de d&#x00E9;cider de l&#x2019;abrogation.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-25", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1N000476?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "Z3", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}